{"tid":464602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[皆大歡喜]通過施政報告致謝議案後,梁君彥代楊岳橋宣布結婚請飲! !","createTime":"2017-11-10T16:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T20:43:57.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5335251a12e1db2cd04554357351271cf7db72","tid":464602,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171110/s00001/1510320181284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171110%2Fs00001%2F1510320181284&d=v7tCjXvSgzELQr0%2BGK7bPEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c5d00468\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171110%2Fs00001%2F1510320181284&h=1b8bae95\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171110/s00001/1510320181284</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會今晚通過《施政報告》致謝議案，係9年來首次。但主席梁君彥宣布議案通過之後，突然叫在席議員留步，睇緊直播嘅Emily都嚇一嚇，諗緊佢有咩大事要宣布。結果，原來梁君彥係要話畀各位議員知，今年較早時喺丹麥結婚嘅公民黨議員楊岳橋（AY），下個月8號擺酒請飲，邀請大家出席。<br />\n相關報道：立法會9年來首次通過《施政報告》致謝議案<br />\n<br />\n但係睇返梁君彥當時嘅發言：「郭榮鏗議員就要求我宣布，幫楊岳橋議員（宣布），喺12月8日佢會有個結婚酒會請各位」，仲話喺平靜之後「有啲嘢去沖喜，大家都好開心」。AY聽到呢個宣布，就即刻喺座位彈起身向其他議員鞠躬合十致謝，其他議員就忍唔住大笑。<br />\n<br />\n但係點解係郭榮鏗叫梁君彥宣布嘅？AY嘅議員辦事處同事就喺facebook專頁「810扮工室」解釋，原來AY事前都唔知情，「係郭榮鏗搞事」，仲喺帖文入面標籤咗郭榮鏗，郭榮鏗轉發帖文時，就加上一個「馬騮掩嘴」嘅表情符號回應。<br />\n唔少網民就留言恭喜AY同埋楊太，仲有人問「收到12月8日&hellip;&hellip;係咪全港市民聽到都有份㗎？」Emily都喺度恭喜AY夫婦，祝福兩位百年好合，早生貴子。"},{"pid":"c24417362d13c59cd43225eec00ff0d824374584","tid":464602,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:19:34.000Z","msg":"歡樂抗爭"},{"pid":"46f7f4df6a85ed71ea680eb5758c73e19f9b14e2","tid":464602,"uid":51920,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"成班圍威餵 做完場戲又叫反對黨"},{"pid":"3850616226473f9fc622e64fa5de9cd497d34f69","tid":464602,"uid":112308,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母，成班議員根本就係夾埋做戲撚香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dd106cfd93f6353072395e7bedcd99527ef7b5","tid":464602,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b0468b4829a8e65ef96d6dd9540b0c94be3194","tid":464602,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"議員呢個身份係下次選舉前<br />\n係冇得收工<br />\n唔該分清楚敵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda636bb2ee5d2acc29ba0c1f92880cca5fd7236","tid":464602,"uid":48670,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"11 Nov 近期活躍五毛<br />\n1. 達哥<br />\n2. 蘋果日報<br />\n3. 侵孫女-阿拉貝拉<br />\n4. 梁天琦<br />\n5. 郭榮鏗<br />\n6. 楊岳橋"},{"pid":"1d8d2595e5dfe53f25431073a345920aa48fb4df","tid":464602,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"唔怪得佢嗰席咁關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b886ed999e71d4a6eb8e79d774a035533e1783d","tid":464602,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"On9到震"},{"pid":"a12680b06c6e3c07e3b0c8575056330cb43f8785","tid":464602,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"鬧劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a896ca55c3800365cf8e2bbdd709fe1605ba7c","tid":464602,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c17c98a056290fcc6050f7926edda26aecafb0c","tid":464602,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:10:40.000Z","msg":"講咁耐相都冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/